text: Bernadette Schober (born 15 July 1984) is a road cyclist from Austria. She won the Austrian National Road Race Championships in 2003. She represented her nation at the 2005 and 2006 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1984 births Category:Austrian female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
